22
00:00:46,173 --> 00:00:57,737
[SPEAKER_06]: The committee has invited Attorney Sharon Everett from KP Law, Finance Director Bob Dickinson, Chief of Staff Dina Nazarian, representatives from the Office of Prevention and Outreach, and representatives from the Office of Planning, Development, and Sustainability to attend this meeting.

23
00:00:58,317 --> 00:01:01,360
[SPEAKER_06]: For further information, aids and accommodations, contact the city clerk at 781-393-2425.

24
