25
00:01:06,545 --> 00:01:17,955
[SPEAKER_06]: So the council has before us a draft ordinance regarding the housing stability notification language that has been in committee and is coming to the committee of the whole for the first time.

26
00:01:18,055 --> 00:01:23,841
[SPEAKER_06]: We have also some comments from attorney Everett that came to our inboxes earlier today.

27
00:01:24,806 --> 00:01:30,013
