44
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:15,865
[SPEAKER_05]: The other thing that we mainly focused on in our last subcommittee meeting, which was in November,

45
00:04:16,687 --> 00:04:25,133
[SPEAKER_05]: was asking legal counsel for a review of the ordinance and also a couple specific questions from the enforcement section.

46
00:04:26,634 --> 00:04:34,600
[SPEAKER_05]: One being, if there are fines associated with noncompliance with the ordinance.

47
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:45,247
[SPEAKER_05]: So the question was, in the event of an unpaid fine, can the city issue a lien if there is a kind of ongoing noncompliance issue with the property owner

48
