[SPEAKER_05]: And you guys are the experts.

272
00:25:48,372 --> 00:25:55,478
[SPEAKER_05]: We're really grateful to have your support, both your support for the ordinance and your support in making sure that it's the right ordinance for our community.

273
00:25:57,560 --> 00:26:02,463
[SPEAKER_05]: So I would like to make two motions, and the first is just a small one.

