[SPEAKER_05]: from section 42, sorry, section 4932.

279
00:26:27,258 --> 00:26:32,242
[SPEAKER_07]: Mr. Kirk, do you have that language?

280
00:26:32,262 --> 00:26:40,228
[SPEAKER_07]: Madam President, I have Councilor Collins moving to strike the definition of property from section 4932.

281
00:26:40,348 --> 00:26:48,875
[SPEAKER_05]: And just for clarity for those, in case I didn't explain it well the first time, we defined the term and then we used it nowhere in the ordinance.

282
00:26:48,895 --> 00:26:50,396
[SPEAKER_05]: So that's why we're just cleaning that up.

283
00:26:50,436 --> 00:26:51,517
[SPEAKER_05]: But that's why I'm proposing to clean it up.

